Package io.github.jy95.fds.r4.functions

Class RangeToStringR4

java.lang.Object
io.github.jy95.fds.r4.functions.RangeToStringR4
All Implemented Interfaces:
RangeToString<FDSConfigR4,org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Range>
public class RangeToStringR4 extends Object implements RangeToString<FDSConfigR4,org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Range>
R4 class for converting range objects to human-readable strings. Implements the Bill Pugh Singleton pattern for thread-safe lazy initialization.
Author:
jy95
